column5: Hey Guys,  Does anyone know a way, or a website that can rip youtube videos off the site, and into a file? So that I can watch as a saved file.  Any help is appreciated!  Thanks, Pachone

I have been using real player to down load all my music off utube(try to get the vids with lyrics,much faster and takes up less space). Get the most updated. I just down load them,then burn to cd,then get rid of it off my pc,then burn the cd back on my pc.Pretty easy,even for me.LOL
